<text><body>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0310c14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0310c15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0310c16" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 954B</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0310c17" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><note n="0310060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】明本，此經麗宋元三本無之，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note>一字頂輪王念誦儀軌<note place="inline">依《忉利天宮所說經》譯</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0310c18" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0310c19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0310c1901">我今說無比力超勝世間出世間真言上上
<lb n="0310c20" ed="T"/>一切佛頂<note n="0310061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王佛＝主宰一字ィ【甲】</note><note n="0310061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王佛【大】，主宰一字【校異-甲】</note><app n="0310061"><lem wit="【大】">王佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">主宰一字</rdg></app>頂輪王念誦儀則。行者先當
<pb n="0311a" ed="T" xml:id="T19.0954B.0311a"/>
<lb n="0311a01" ed="T"/>清淨，於淨處安本尊像，面西稽首禮，受三歸，
<lb n="0311a02" ed="T"/>捨身說罪，受戒，發菩提心，隨喜勸請發願廻
<lb n="0311a03" ed="T"/>向已。應結佛部三昧耶印：四頂互內交，二輪
<lb n="0311a04" ed="T"/>並合竪，前附於蓋，是名一切如來心印。真言
<lb n="0311a05" ed="T"/>曰：</p>
<lb n="0311a06" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311a0601">「唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　邇那匿<note place="inline">而翼切</note><note place="inline">二</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311a07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311a0701">次結蓮<note n="0311001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">華＋（部）【甲】</note><note n="0311001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">華【大】，華部【甲】</note><app n="0311001"><lem wit="【大】">華</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">華部</rdg></app>三昧耶印：即前印，左輪屈入掌
<lb n="0311a08" ed="T"/>中，右輪如前竪，是名蓮華部心印。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311a09" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311a0901">「唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　阿嚕力<note place="inline">二</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311a10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311a1001">次結金剛部三昧耶印：即前蓮華部心印，右
<lb n="0311a11" ed="T"/>輪屈入掌中，左輪依前竪，是名金剛部心印。
<lb n="0311a12" ed="T"/>真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311a13" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311a1301">「唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>地力<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">二</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311a1401">次結甲冑印准根本印：屈二蓋拄二光，背印
<lb n="0311a15" ed="T"/>額右肩左肩心喉五處。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311a16" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311a1601">「唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　斫羯囉<note place="inline">二合</note>靺<g ref="#CB00069"/>底<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">二</note>　鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>賒弭多
<lb n="0311a17" ed="T"/><note place="inline">三</note>　囉捺囉<note place="inline">二合，引</note>囉捺囉<note place="inline">二合，引</note><note place="inline">四</note>　婆<note place="inline">去聲</note>娑摩<note place="inline">二合</note>車盧
<lb n="0311a18" ed="T"/>瑟尼<note place="inline">二合</note>沙<note place="inline">五</note>　囉乞沙<note place="inline">二合</note>囉乞沙<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0311002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鋡＝<g ref="#CB00805"/>【甲】</note><note n="0311002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鋡【大】，<g ref="#CB00805"/>【甲】</note><g ref="#CB00805"/><note place="inline">六</note>　吽
<lb n="0311a19" ed="T"/>癹娑嚩<note place="inline">二合合</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">七</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311a2001">次結佛眼印：二手合掌，屈二蓋各拄光背，二
<lb n="0311a21" ed="T"/>輪屈入掌，印五處。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311a22" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311a2201">「娜<note n="0311003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謨＝莫【甲】＊</note><note n="0311003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謨【大】＊，莫【甲】＊</note><app n="0311003"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>　唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">二</note>　嚕嚕薩怖<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0311a23" ed="T"/>嚕<note place="inline">三</note>　入嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>攞底瑟姹<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">四</note>　悉馱盧者寧<note place="inline">五</note>　薩
<lb n="0311a24" ed="T"/>嚩喇他<note place="inline">二合</note>娑達尼娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">六</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311a25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311a2501">次結大海印：二手內相叉，仰掌擘開二輪，右
<lb n="0311a26" ed="T"/>旋三匝想大海。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311a27" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311a2701">「唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　微摩盧娜地娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">二</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311a2801">次於大海中想須彌盧山，四寶所成，二手內
<lb n="0311a29" ed="T"/>相叉，急握豎拳。真言曰：</p>
<pb n="0311b" ed="T" xml:id="T19.0954B.0311b"/>
<lb n="0311b01" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311b0101">「唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　阿者攞吽<note place="inline">二</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311b0201">次於須彌盧山上想寶樓閣，加持寶樓閣<note n="0311004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔印〕－【甲】</note><note n="0311004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0311004"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，
<lb n="0311b03" ed="T"/>印二手金剛掌。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311b04" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311b0401">「娜<app type="star" corresp="#0311003"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　唵薩嚩他欠<note place="inline">二</note>　鄔娜
<lb n="0311b05" ed="T"/>哦<note place="inline">二合</note>帝薩頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉呬<note place="inline">引</note><g ref="#CB00805"/><note place="inline">三</note>　哦哦那檢娑嚩
<lb n="0311b06" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">四</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311b07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311b0701">次結佛頂輪王印：二掌內相叉作拳，竪二光
<lb n="0311b08" ed="T"/>屈上節如劍，並竪二輪屈二蓋兩節，相拄於
<lb n="0311b09" ed="T"/>二輪上，印五處加護。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311b10" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311b1001">「娜<app type="star" corresp="#0311003"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>　步嚕唵<note place="inline">三合</note><note place="inline">二</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311b1101">次結網橛印：准前根本印，屈二蓋上節，背不
<lb n="0311b12" ed="T"/>相著，以二輪各壓，上下揮轉，即成結上下界。
<lb n="0311b13" ed="T"/>真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311b14" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311b1401">「娜<app type="star" corresp="#0311003"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>　阿鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0311b15" ed="T"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>　唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">三</note>　微枳囉拏微特防<note place="inline">去聲二合</note>娑尼<note place="inline">四</note>
<lb n="0311b16" ed="T"/>　迦比羅貳縛里尼<note place="inline">五</note>　怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>娑耶<note place="inline">六</note>　嚩日囉<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0311b17" ed="T"/>合</note>吠賒薩帝呶<note place="inline">引</note>囉特縛<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">七</note>　能<note place="inline">上聲</note>瑟吒囉<note place="inline">三合</note>
<lb n="0311b18" ed="T"/>囉乞沙<note place="inline">二合</note><g ref="#CB00805"/>癹<note place="inline"><note n="0311005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八＋（吽）ィ本文【甲】</note><note n="0311005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八【大】，八吽【校異-甲】</note><app n="0311005"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">八吽</rdg></app></note>」</p>
<lb n="0311b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311b1901">次結牆印：准前根本印，屈二蓋兩節相逼，平
<lb n="0311b20" ed="T"/>竪二輪附二蓋，右旋三匝即成。金剛牆界真
<lb n="0311b21" ed="T"/>言曰<note place="inline">歸命同前</note>：</p>
<lb n="0311b22" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311b2201">「噁<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　莫壑<note place="inline">二</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311b2301">次結車輅印：二手內相叉，仰掌申二蓋，令甲
<lb n="0311b24" ed="T"/>側相拄，屈二輪拄蓋根下，想於他方世界奉
<lb n="0311b25" ed="T"/>迎本尊。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311b26" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311b2601">「唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　覩嚕覩嚕吽<note place="inline">二</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311b2701">次結迎輅印：准車輅印，以二輪撥光頭，向身
<lb n="0311b28" ed="T"/>三招。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311b29" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311b2901">「發遣除羯哩灑<note place="inline">二合</note>耶加尾薩哩惹耶</p>
<pb n="0311c" ed="T" xml:id="T19.0954B.0311c"/>
<lb n="0311c01" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311c0101">「娜<app type="star" corresp="#0311003"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>薩底哩野<note place="inline"><note n="0311006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝四【甲】</note><note n="0311006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，四【甲】</note><app n="0311006"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">四</rdg></app>合</note>地尾<note place="inline">二合</note>迦南<note place="inline">一</note>　怛他孽
<lb n="0311c02" ed="T"/>哆南<note place="inline">二</note>　唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">三</note>　嚩日啷<note place="inline">二合</note>儗<note place="inline">愚以切</note>儞也<note place="inline">二<note n="0311007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（引）【甲】</note><note n="0311007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】，合引【甲】</note><app n="0311007"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合引</rdg></app></note>羯
<lb n="0311c03" ed="T"/>哩灑耶娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">四</note>」</p>
<lb n="0311c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311c0401">次結迎請印：准前根本印，屈右蓋於光後，向
<lb n="0311c05" ed="T"/>前三招。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311c06" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311c0601">「娜謨婆誐嚩帝<note place="inline">一</note>　阿鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵覩瑟尼<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0311c07" ed="T"/>沙耶<note place="inline">二</note>　翳呬翳<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0311008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑＝呬婆【甲】</note><note n="0311008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娑【大】，呬婆【甲】</note><app n="0311008"><lem wit="【大】">娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">呬婆</rdg></app>誐刎<note place="inline">三</note>　達麼囉惹<note place="inline">平聲</note>鉢
