<lb n="0311c12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311c1201">次結一切<note n="0311010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辨＝辦【甲】</note><note n="0311010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辨【大】，辦【甲】</note><app n="0311010"><lem wit="【大】">辨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">辦</rdg></app>事佛頂印：二手內相叉，竪二光
