<lb n="0311c14" ed="T"/>言。加持辟除去垢結界皆用此真言。左旋辟
<lb n="0311c15" ed="T"/>除，右旋結界。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0311c16" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0311c1601">「娜<app type="star" corresp="#0311003"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三滿多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>　唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">二</note>　吒嚕<note n="0311011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚕＝唵【甲】</note><note n="0311011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚕【大】，唵【甲】</note><app n="0311011"><lem wit="【大】">嚕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唵</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">三</note>　滿
