<lb n="0311c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311c1801">次重結前網橛印，結上方界。</p>
<lb n="0311c19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0311c1901">次結阿娑莽倪<note place="inline">移枳切</note>尼印：側二手，左掩右，<note n="0311012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">堅＝竪【甲】</note><note n="0311012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">堅【大】，竪【甲】</note><app n="0311012"><lem wit="【大】">堅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">竪</rdg></app>
