<lb n="0312c03" ed="T"/>沙耶<note place="inline">四</note>　薩嚩尾伽那<note place="inline">二合</note>尾<note n="0312004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持＝特【甲】</note><note n="0312004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持【大】，特【甲】</note><app n="0312004"><lem wit="【大】">持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">特</rdg></app>望<note place="inline">二合</note>娑那迦
<lb n="0312c04" ed="T"/>囉耶<note place="inline">五</note>　怛嚧<note place="inline">二合</note>吒耶娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">六</note>」</p>
<lb n="0312c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0312c0501">次結輪王佛頂心印：准前根本印，屈二蓋拄
<lb n="0312c06" ed="T"/>二光上節<note n="0312005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">節＝背【甲】</note><note n="0312005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">節【大】，背【甲】</note><app n="0312005"><lem wit="【大】">節</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">背</rdg></app>上。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0312c07" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0312c0701">「娜<app type="star" corresp="#0311003"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>　阿鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312c08" ed="T"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>　唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">三</note>　怛他<note n="0312006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩那＝蘖都【甲】</note><note n="0312006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">薩那【大】，蘖都【甲】</note><app n="0312006"><lem wit="【大】">薩那</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蘖都</rdg></app>瑟尼<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0312007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沙＋（阿）【甲】</note><note n="0312007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沙【大】，沙阿【甲】</note><app n="0312007"><lem wit="【大】">沙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">沙阿</rdg></app>那嚩
<lb n="0312c09" ed="T"/>盧枳多<note place="inline">四</note>　沒馱尼斫羯囉<note place="inline">二合</note>靺<g ref="#CB00069"/>底<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">五</note>　吽入
<lb n="0312c10" ed="T"/>嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>羅入嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>羅<note place="inline">六</note>　馱迦馱迦<note place="inline">七</note>　度那微度
<lb n="0312c11" ed="T"/>那<note place="inline">八</note>　怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>娑耶麼囉逾瑳囉耶<note place="inline">九</note>　呵那呵那
<lb n="0312c12" ed="T"/><note place="inline">十</note>　伴惹伴惹<note place="inline">十一</note>　暗<note n="0312008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">音＝惡【甲】</note><note n="0312008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">音【大】，惡【甲】</note><app n="0312008"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">惡</rdg></app><note n="0312009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text"><g ref="#CB03543"/>＋（十二）夾註【甲】</note><note n="0312009" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><g ref="#CB03543"/>【大】，<g ref="#CB03543"/><note place="inline">十二</note>【甲】</note><app n="0312009"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB03543"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><g ref="#CB03543"/><note place="inline">十二</note></rdg></app>鉢嚨<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline"><note n="0312010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十二〕－【甲】</note><note n="0312010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十二【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0312010"><lem wit="【大】">十二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>　企尼君
<lb n="0312c13" ed="T"/>吒哩尼<note place="inline">十三</note>　阿鉢囉爾多薩怛囉馱哩尼<note place="inline">十四</note>　吽
<lb n="0312c14" ed="T"/>癹娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">十五</note>」</p>
<lb n="0312c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0312c1501">次結心<note n="0312011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中＋（心）【甲】</note><note n="0312011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中【大】，中心【甲】</note><app n="0312011"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">中心</rdg></app>印：准前根本印，屈二蓋加於二光
<lb n="0312c16" ed="T"/>上節上。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0312c17" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0312c1701">「娜<app type="star" corresp="#0311003"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>　阿鉢囉<note place="inline">一合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312c18" ed="T"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>　唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">三</note>　阿鉢囉<note place="inline">引</note>爾多特<note place="inline">地翼切</note><note place="inline">四</note>」</p>
<lb n="0312c19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0312c1901">普通諸佛頂印：二手虛心<note n="0312012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔金剛〕ィ－【甲】</note><note n="0312012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">金剛【大】，〔－〕【校異-甲】</note><app n="0312012"><lem wit="【大】">金剛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>合掌，如華在
<lb n="0312c20" ed="T"/>掌中，行者若怱遽不能遍結諸佛頂印，但結
<lb n="0312c21" ed="T"/>此印誦諸佛頂真言。</p><p xml:id="pT19p0312c2109" cb:place="inline">次結頂印：准前根本印，
<lb n="0312c22" ed="T"/>屈右蓋竪，於右光後，令不相著。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0312c23" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0312c2301">「娜<app type="star" corresp="#0311003"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>　阿鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312c24" ed="T"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>　唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">三</note>　斫羯囉<note place="inline">二合</note>靺<g ref="#CB00069"/>底<note place="inline">二合</note>唵吽<note place="inline">四</note>」</p>
<lb n="0312c25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0312c2501">次結頭印：准前根本印，開二蓋各直竪於光
<lb n="0312c26" ed="T"/>後，令不相著微屈。真言曰<note place="inline">歸命同前</note>：</p>
<lb n="0312c27" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0312c2701">「唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　斫羯囉<note place="inline">二合</note>靺<g ref="#CB00069"/>底<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">二</note>　吽癹娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶
<lb n="0312c28" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">三</note>」</p>
<lb n="0312c29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0312c2901">次又結根本印。</p>
<pb n="0313a" ed="T" xml:id="T19.0954B.0313a"/>
<lb n="0313a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0313a0101">次結大三昧耶印，加護本尊：二手內相叉，竪
<lb n="0313a02" ed="T"/>二光，屈二蓋於光後如鉤，相去一穬麥許，二
<lb n="0313a03" ed="T"/>輪各附蓋根下，右旋三匝。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0313a04" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0313a0401">「唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　商羯哩<note place="inline">二</note>　摩訶三昧鹽娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">三</note>」</p>
<lb n="0313a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0313a0501">次誦一百八名讚歎。</p>
<lb n="0313a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0313a0601">欲念誦，先以五支成本尊，或五相成本尊瑜
<lb n="0313a07" ed="T"/>伽，或於<note n="0313001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">處＝三【甲】</note><note n="0313001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">處【大】，三【甲】</note><app n="0313001"><lem wit="【大】">處</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">三</rdg></app>處<note place="inline">頂舌心也</note>想一字頂輪成，本尊坐八
<lb n="0313a08" ed="T"/>葉蓮華，於一一葉上想七寶，<note n="0313002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">准＝唯【甲】</note><note n="0313002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">准【大】，唯【甲】</note><app n="0313002"><lem wit="【大】">准</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唯</rdg></app>前蓮華葉
<lb n="0313a09" ed="T"/>上想佛眼尊。次應持珠<note place="inline">此依《菩提場所說經》</note>。</p>
<lb n="0313a10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0313a1001">次持珠合掌，捧珠誦清珠真言七遍。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0313a11" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0313a1101">「唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　阿娜步<note place="inline">二合</note>低尾惹曳<note place="inline">而<note n="0313003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">矣＝奚【甲】</note><note n="0313003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">矣【大】，奚【甲】</note><app n="0313003"><lem wit="【大】">矣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">奚</rdg></app>切</note><note place="inline">二</note>　悉地悉馱囉
<lb n="0313a12" ed="T"/>梯娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">三</note>」</p>
<lb n="0313a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0313a1301">次結持珠印：二手各以輪捻高甲，直竪二光
<lb n="0313a14" ed="T"/>二勝，屈二蓋於光後，令不相著<note place="inline">如《毘盧遮那經》半金剛杵印</note>
<lb n="0313a15" ed="T"/>真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0313a16" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0313a1601">「娜謨婆誐嚩底<note place="inline">一</note>　蘇悉第娑馱耶<note place="inline">二</note>　悉馱囉梯
<lb n="0313a17" ed="T"/>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">三</note>」</p>
<lb n="0313a18" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0313a1801" type="regular"><l>次應淨其心，<caesura/>如法而念誦，</l>
<lb n="0313a19" ed="T"/><l>持珠令當心，<caesura/>繫心於鼻端。</l>
<lb n="0313a20" ed="T"/><l>字句分明呼，<caesura/>不緩亦不急，</l>
<lb n="0313a21" ed="T"/><l>不頻伸噦嗌，<caesura/>咳嗽與唾涕。</l>
<lb n="0313a22" ed="T"/><l>染等心相應，<caesura/>及心緣苦受，</l>
<lb n="0313a23" ed="T"/><l>如是等過患，<caesura/>皆不得成就。</l></lg>
<lb n="0313a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0313a2401">當念誦時，身心不得疲怠，若勞倦即應結五
<lb n="0313a25" ed="T"/>供養印，誦讚歎獻閼伽。念誦畢持珠頂上，次
<lb n="0313a26" ed="T"/>結前密縫印，左轉一匝即成解界。</p>
<lb n="0313a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0313a2701">次結奉送印：准前根本印，左蓋外擲，誦迎請
<lb n="0313a28" ed="T"/>真言，除「翳呬翳呬」，加「孽車孽車」句，即成奉送。
<lb n="0313a29" ed="T"/>次應復結牆及網橛等印，加護處上下及所
<pb n="0313b" ed="T" xml:id="T19.0954B.0313b"/>
<lb n="0313b01" ed="T"/>成就物。</p><p xml:id="pT19p0313b0104" cb:place="inline">次結計里枳里印：左輪壓勝甲上，餘
<lb n="0313b02" ed="T"/>三指頂坼開直竪，如三股杵形，右旋轉三匝
<lb n="0313b03" ed="T"/>成結界。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0313b04" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0313b0401">「唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>　枳里枳里嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吽癹<note place="inline">二</note>」</p>
<lb n="0313b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0313b0501">次結軍吒利印：二勝於掌中交，屈二高壓，
<lb n="0313b06" ed="T"/>以二輪壓高上，竪二光相合，屈二蓋於光
<lb n="0313b07" ed="T"/>後，令一麥許不相著，右旋三匝即成結界。真
<lb n="0313b08" ed="T"/>言曰：</p>
<lb n="0313b09" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0313b0901">「娜謨囉怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>夜耶<note place="inline">一</note>　娜<note n="0313004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謨＝莫ィ【甲】＊</note><note n="0313004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謨【大】＊，莫【校異-甲】＊</note><app n="0313004"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">莫</rdg></app>室戰<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0313b10" ed="T"/>合</note>拏嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>波拏曳<note place="inline">二</note>　摩訶藥乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>細
<lb n="0313b11" ed="T"/>那波多曳<note place="inline">三</note>　娜<app type="star" corresp="#0313004"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">莫</rdg></app>室戰<note place="inline">二合</note>拏嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>句
<lb n="0313b12" ed="T"/><g ref="#CB00080"/>馱耶<note place="inline">四</note>　唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">五</note>　虎嚕虎嚕<note place="inline">六</note>　底瑟姹<note place="inline">二合</note>底瑟
<lb n="0313b13" ed="T"/>姹<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">七</note>　滿馱滿馱<note place="inline">八</note>　呵那呵那<note place="inline">九</note>　阿蜜哩<note place="inline">二合</note>帝
<lb n="0313b14" ed="T"/>吽癹娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">十</note>」</p>
<lb n="0313b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0313b1501">從一字真言，至於十五字，每計於字數，一字
<lb n="0313b16" ed="T"/>一洛叉，乃至三十字，應誦三<note n="0313005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十〕－【甲】</note><note n="0313005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0313005"><lem wit="【大】">十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>洛叉。應作
<lb n="0313b17" ed="T"/>先事法，三十字已上，應誦一萬遍。</p>
<lb n="0313b18" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>一字頂輪王念誦儀軌<note n="0313006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本奧書云貞享三年丙寅之初秋念三在武城乾隅多聞室裏一挍訓點河南延命苾芻淨嚴熏沐拜手，昔日從師親受傳今乘絳帳強弘宣擴充一字周沙界沾溉何曾限大千，元祿十五年十二月十二日以淨嚴大和尚之本再挍了尊教</note><anchor type="circle"/></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>